{"tid":1910512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家支唔支持鄺神話派1萬比新移民?","createTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-04T18:30:24.000Z","uid":50275,"like":4,"dislike":47,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"b8ffde99ca38115c145616cc858a723acc1a2744","tid":1910512,"uid":50275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:16:15.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512346-20200304.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512346-20200304.htm&d=%2BOqOIcZVGdgLhUso5zZbIMFcVrLE0QCYyCuC44%2F36M0%3D&h=39a7b7bd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1512346-20200304.htm&h=296e00fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1512346-20200304.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n鄧家彪認為關愛基金派1萬元應涵蓋少數族裔人士<br />\n<br />\n政府今明兩日合共派出4班包機到湖北武漢接載港人回港。<br />\n<br />\n工聯會新界東辦事處總幹事鄧家彪表示，首批返港的人只佔整體滯留港人大約兩成，知道有一名孕婦未能乘搭今次包機，因為由她在湖北居住的城市到武漢機場，即使是「點對點」交通接送都需要6個多小時，希望特區政府日後能夠再派出包機到湖北其他機場，接載滯留當地的港人，例如宜昌機場。<br />\n<br />\n另外，政府計劃透過關愛基金向非永久居民發放1 萬元，主要是持單程證和新來港作家庭團聚的人士。本身是關愛基金專責小組成員的鄧家彪認為，派發對象應該涵蓋少數族裔人士。他又說，如果7月接受申請，預計要到10月市民才收到錢。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另一名關愛基金成員、民主黨立法會議員鄺俊宇說，是否向新移民發放1萬元，關鍵是對方有沒有真正需要，希望錢能夠盡快到有需要市民手上</span>。他又指，預算案與關愛基金派錢是兩回事，應該要分開處理，認為關愛基金應該「開倉」向更多有需要市民派錢，但如何發放則需要再商討。<br />\n<br />\n支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n反對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"628e96a2c185c2617efb5e71df048937c21ceb57","tid":1910512,"uid":2429,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:17:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wb5n3jL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fwb5n3jL.gif&h=67f25a89&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df8278b609606ff598565c31e54679bc61edad05","tid":1910512,"uid":147895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:19:28.000Z","msg":"唔支持"},{"pid":"bd5998c8bb1d994c2324f05ee4744647b6a1d84f","tid":1910512,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:19:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f21f28e3836662ec689d814cacbd0671b3bfc73","tid":1910512,"uid":34084,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:21:41.000Z","msg":"痴撚線 成班對香港社會冇貢獻嘅蝗蟲攞撚盡曬福利<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00c6ae60249baf212166e541cfda55f3b05beb84","tid":1910512,"uid":23094,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:21:49.000Z","msg":"呢段嘢邊度講佢話派俾新移民？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命<br />\n五大訴求 缺一不可<br />\n沒有普選 唯有獨立<br />\n加入工會 全民三罷</span></span>"},{"pid":"47c37b879c9eb6446b6475006890b55aab63eaa8","tid":1910512,"uid":191453,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:14.000Z","msg":"唔支持 但不否定佢之前的付出"},{"pid":"d1fbae8f981de26882d22bcd69b5600b95c340a7","tid":1910512,"uid":293648,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:22:15.000Z","msg":"武漢個d拎住香港身分證講普通話<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f429687c1a348c9cd675c91bae590429b7dfe559","tid":1910512,"uid":269481,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:25:29.000Z","msg":"總之冇三粒星就唔派得<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c954743bc757ca7f51d5ae44e9ffcca17d999f1f","tid":1910512,"uid":54642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:29:57.000Z","msg":"唔支持"},{"pid":"40edb8b43eb13f7fc4313a31eb890b943c79d257","tid":1910512,"uid":227275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-04T17:31:22.000Z","msg":"派比新移民OK<br />\n不過係投資移民果堆"},{"pid":"93c55fd2c614181